Service Layer: Facilitates secure access to on-premise or external databases, enabling the extension to retrieve schema information like tables, views, and stored procedures without direct user intervention.

Language Model Integration: Utilizes a powerful LLM to interpret natural language inputs and generate accurate SQL/NoSQL queries, bridging the gap between non-technical users and complex database querying.

Error Handling and Feedback: Includes robust error-handling mechanisms at each step—from schema retrieval to query execution—ensuring users receive actionable feedback in case of issues, enhancing reliability and usability.
